bib_record.title: Observation of two-hole states at high excitation energy in (p,t) reactions

free_txt: Angular distributions for the bumps were measured in
the Nd-146(p,t)Nd-144,Zr-94(p,t)Zr-92 and Zn-68(p,t)
reactions at laboratory angles between 6 and about 60
degrees.
The uncertainty in the absolute cross
sections. No information about source of uncertainty.
Error from bars on fig. No information
about source of uncertainty.
Figures quality in this paper is second-rate.
Negative number in data-section is result of figures
quality.

thickness of 3-4 mg/cm2. The isotopic purities was
higher than 95%.
